/** * Expert: allows you to customize the {@link * FieldType}. *

NOTE: the provided byte[] is not copied so be sure * not to change it until you're done with this field. * @param name field name * @param bytes byte array pointing to binary content (not copied) * @param type custom {@link FieldType} for this field * @throws IllegalArgumentException if the field name, value or type * is null. */ public StoredField(String name, BytesRef bytes, FieldType type) { super(name, bytes, type); }
